# 🔥 Tech Lead Engineering Standards v2.1 (AI-Executable & Production-Ready)

---

## 0. Non-Negotiables (Fail = Block PR / Halt Execution)
- ❌ No tests → no merge
- ❌ No input validation → no merge
- ❌ Hidden side effects → no merge
- ❌ Breaking API/contracts → no merge
- ❌ Sensitive data in logs → no merge
- ❌ Unreadable code → no merge
- 🚫 **Code, variables, comments, commits, and documentation MUST be in English**
- 🌍 **All UI strings, errors, and user-facing text MUST support i18n (pt-BR, es-ES)**
- ️ **Every successful build/test cycle MUST trigger automatic VPS deployment**
- 🔑 **`.env` must be auto-validated, templated, and injected securely during deploy**
- 🛑 **Never modify database schema or delete data without explicit written approval**

